$$
\begin{aligned}
c \dot y + k y &= c \, A \frac {\pi v} {L} \cos \frac {\pi v} {L}t + k \, A \sin \frac {\pi v} {L}t \\
&= A_0 \sin (\omega_f t - \phi_0) \\
\text{where} &\quad
A_0 = A \sqrt {(c \, \frac {\pi v} {L})^2+k^2}, \phi_0 = \arctan \frac {\pi cv} {k L}, \omega_f = \frac {\pi v} {L}
\end{aligned}
$$
